FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (

        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"

    JOIN pg_catalog.pg_namespace n ON n.oid=c.relnamespace
    WHERE n.nspname='public' AND
          c.relname='__EFMigrationsHistory'
)

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))

    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"

) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"

    SELECT 1

    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0

    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"

    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"

2024-10-02 09:56:44.006 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"

        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))

FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))

    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))

2024-10-02 10:34:15.448 +04:00 [WRN] Compiling a query which loads related collections for more than one collection navigation, either via 'Include' or through projection, but no 'QuerySplittingBehavior' has been configured. 2024-10-02 10:34:15.461 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (8ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

SELECT r."Id", r."Name", r."Description", r."IsActive", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Name", t0."Description", t0."RoleId", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Name0", t0."Path", t0."Description0", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id00"
FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
ORDER BY r."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."EndpointGroupId", t0."Id", t0."EndpointGroupId0", t0."Id0"

FROM "Roles" AS r
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT r1."EndpointGroupId", e2."Name", e2."Description", r1."RoleId", e2."Id", t."Id" AS "Id0", t."Name" AS "Name0", t."Path", t."Description" AS "Description0", t."EndpointGroupId" AS "EndpointGroupId0", t."Id0" AS "Id00"
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r1
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e2 ON r1."EndpointGroupId" = e2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT e3."EndpointId" AS "Id", e4."Name", e4."Path", e4."Description", e3."EndpointGroupId", e4."Id" AS "Id0"
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e3
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e4 ON e3."EndpointId" = e4."Id"
    ) AS t ON e2."Id" = t."EndpointGroupId"
) AS t0 ON r."Id" = t0."RoleId"
WHERE r."IsActive" AND NOT (r."IsDeleted") AND r."IsActive" AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "RoleEndpointGroups" AS r0
    INNER JOIN "EndpointGroups" AS e ON r0."EndpointGroupId" = e."Id"
    WHERE r."Id" = r0."RoleId" AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "EndpointGroupEndpoints" AS e0
        INNER JOIN "Endpoints" AS e1 ON e0."EndpointId" = e1."Id"
        WHERE e."Id" = e0."EndpointGroupId" AND NOT (e1."IsDeleted") AND e1."IsActive"))
